==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Bespeak
<hw>Be*speak"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A bespeaking. Among actors, a
benefit (when a particular play is bespoken.)</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The night of
her <xex>bespeak</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Dickens.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bespeaker</ent>⟦br⟧
